    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents a composite attack item that groups multiple <ref refid="class_mandatory2_d_game_framework_1_1model_1_1attack_1_1_attack_item" kindref="compound">AttackItem</ref> instances into a single logical weapon. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class implements the Composite design pattern, allowing multiple attack items to be treated as a single item. The composite sums the Hit, Range, and Weight values of all contained items. It can be used by creatures to represent carrying or equipping multiple weapons at once. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
